      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAKE FRIENDS (4) started a hot favourite at Bathurst last start but manners let her down. Tackled the NSW Oaks series prior where she placed behind the eventual winner in the heats. If she performs to that level she may prove too good for these. STAR TO FALL (9) was a beaten favourite last start at Melton but she was forced to work when racing three wide without cover so did well to stick on for a 1.7m second. Draws deep but was sound when midfield in an Oaks heat here two back. WHERES MY REASON (8) deserves respect off a brave last-start win where she drew on the back row and raced three wide without cover but toughed it out. HIGHINDELIGHT (6) could be close to a win following back-to-back placings at this circuit and distance, the latest from a wider barrier.",
